Spec: Fetch Client
Purpose:
  Provide a Node fetch adapter for HTTP requests.

Structure:
  fetch-client.ts: Fetch client implementation.
  fetch-client.test.ts: Fetch client tests.

Owns:
  fetch-client.ts
  fetch-client.test.ts

Must:
  Expose get(url).
  Use global fetch by default.
  Accept a fetch implementation through constructor parameters.
  Return status, ok, json(), and bytes() for responses.

Depends on:
  Node.js fetch

Exposes:
  FetchClient.get(url)
  FetchResponse
